---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — DearSQL"
  description="DearSQL privacy policy. We collect minimal data and never sell it."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "Privacy Policy", url: "/privacy" },
  ]}
>
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 text-sm">
    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">## Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-subtext0 text-xs mb-6">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-subtext0">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">### What we collect</h2>
        <p>DearSQL collects minimal data:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>
            - <span class="text-text">Bug reports</span> — submitted voluntarily via
            the "report bug" form. Filed as GitHub issues. Includes your description
            and any screenshots you attach.
          </li>
          <li>
            - <span class="text-text">License validation</span> — when you activate
            a Pro license, your license key and a device identifier are sent to Polar.sh
            to verify the activation. We do not store this on our own servers.
          </li>
          <li>
            - <span class="text-text">Purchase data</span> — handled entirely by Polar.sh.
            We receive your email address when you buy a license. We do not store
            payment details.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">### What we don't collect</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>- No analytics or tracking on this website</li>
          <li>- No telemetry from the desktop app</li>
          <li>- No access to your database credentials or query data</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-bold text-text mb-2">### Third-party services</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>
            - <a href="https://polar.sh" target="_blank">Polar.sh</a> — payment and
            license management
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Each service has its own privacy policy governing data they collect.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
